176
00:09:18.605 --> 00:09:21.770
how your progress against
that goal can be measured.

177
00:09:21.770 --> 00:09:25.160
They will also make you designate

178
00:09:25.160 --> 00:09:27.680
a director on your board

179
00:09:27.680 --> 00:09:30.365
