that impact goal,

180
00:09:30.365 --> 00:09:34.010
and you're also going to be
liable to your investors.

181
00:09:34.010 --> 00:09:36.140
Investors could even sue you over

182
00:09:36.140 --> 00:09:38.990
not pursuing your impact goals.

183
00:09:38.990 --> 00:09:42.335
So they've made
a real legal commitment

184
00:09:42.335 --> 00:09:46.350
to pursuing their impact goal.

185
00:09:47.230 --> 00:09:49.870
As opposed to
just a B Corp that has

186
00:09:49.870 --> 00:09:52.310
got a stamp of approval
from a private outfit,

187
00:09:52.310 --> 00:09:56.840
a benefit corp has actually
legally exposed themselves

188
00:09:56.840 --> 00:09:58.925
to damages if they

189
00:09:58.925 --> 00:10:01.940
don't follow through
on their impact goal.

190
00:10:01.940 --> 00:10:03.565
So those are two things
to look for,

191
00:10:03.565 --> 00:10:06.245
B Corps and then
also benefit corps.

192
