208
00:11:02.345 --> 00:11:05.660
"I'm learning about being

209
00:11:05.660 --> 00:11:08.060
an entrepreneur by following

210
00:11:08.060 --> 00:11:10.755
this investment
once I'm involved."

211
00:11:10.755 --> 00:11:12.840
When you put
those things together,

212
00:11:12.840 --> 00:11:17.240
maybe that helps us
explain why some people

213
00:11:17.240 --> 00:11:19.400
put money into
crowdfunding when just

214
00:11:19.400 --> 00:11:21.680
from a pure financial
point of view,

215
00:11:21.680 --> 00:11:25.200
it could be a hard thing
to pencil out.